    <entry>
      <title>日常生活营养食谱（不定期更新）</title>
      <link href="/2018/04/2018-04-13-YYSP/"/>
      <url>/2018/04/2018-04-13-YYSP/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>每天的家庭生活都是要重复做很多菜，这里做个记录，以便不断优化菜品</p><h3 id="下饭菜"><a href="#下饭菜" class="headerlink" title="下饭菜"></a>下饭菜</h3><p>酸辣土豆丝</p><p>酸辣白菜</p><p>青椒炒肉</p><p>西红柿炒蛋</p><p>韭菜苔炒蛋</p><p>秋葵炒鸡蛋</p><p>可乐鸡翅</p><p>辣子鸡/鸭</p><p>红烧茄子</p><p>辣炒花蛤</p><p>黄焖鸡</p><p>红烧鱼</p><p>肉末豆角</p><p>宫保鸡丁 (还没做过)</p><p>孜然牛肉土豆片 (还没做过)</p><p>手撕包菜 (还没做过)</p><p>干锅菜花 (还没做过)</p><h3 id="凉菜"><a href="#凉菜" class="headerlink" title="凉菜"></a>凉菜</h3><p>凉拌黄瓜</p><p>凉拌海带丝</p><p>凉拌木耳</p><h3 id="煲汤"><a href="#煲汤" class="headerlink" title="煲汤"></a>煲汤</h3><p>鱼头汤/鲫鱼汤</p><p>小鸡炖蘑菇</p><p>冬瓜排骨汤</p><p>[紫菜]西红柿蛋汤</p><h3 id="面食"><a href="#面食" class="headerlink" title="面食"></a>面食</h3><p>焖面</p><p>番茄鸡蛋面</p>]]></content>
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> 日常生活 </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> 生活 </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    <entry>
      <title>建立并加强思维反射</title>
      <link href="/2018/04/%E6%80%9D%E7%BB%B4%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%84/"/>
      <url>/2018/04/%E6%80%9D%E7%BB%B4%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%84/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>将学习过程和能力形成的过程进行分析，在进行新技能的认知过程中，我们可以有迹可循，从而通过形成快速认知习惯加快认知过程本身。</p><a id="more"></a><p>我们不断的学习, 目标可以分为三个阶段：</p><ol><li>进行长久的记忆存储</li><li>讲这些记忆进行关联</li><li>将这些新的关联体进行再次存储</li></ol><p>步骤2可以帮我们理解认知我们学接触到的信息，步骤3是推动这个世界的源力，我们的知识正是千百年来一代一代的人的结晶，通过各种形式把步骤3形成的新关联体以各种形式记录下来。所以我们都是站在巨人的肩膀上。</p><p>社交天才和运动天才在抽象层面上说，其机理几乎如出一辙：一个是思维记忆，另一个是肌肉记忆。</p>]]></content>
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> 所思所想 </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> 瞎想 </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    <entry>
      <title>ReactJS - day01 入门知识</title>
      <link href="/2018/04/ReactJS-day01/"/>
      <url>/2018/04/ReactJS-day01/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>介绍React开发环境的初始化，主要包括：组件定义、props属性、state状态、组件生命周期、事件处理</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="React环境初始化"><a href="#React环境初始化" class="headerlink" title="React环境初始化"></a>React环境初始化</h2><h3 id="入门介绍"><a href="#入门介绍" class="headerlink" title="入门介绍:"></a>入门介绍:</h3><blockquote><p>声明式：数据驱动</p><p>组件化：把相似的代码放到一起进行复用，传递数据</p></blockquote><ul><li><h4 id="官网"><a href="#官网" class="headerlink" title="官网:"></a>官网:</h4></li></ul><blockquote><p>英文:<a href="https://reactjs.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://reactjs.org/</a></p><p>中文:<a href="https://doc.react-china.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://doc.react-china.org/</a></p></blockquote><h3 id="方式一-脚手架-快捷、稳定"><a href="#方式一-脚手架-快捷、稳定" class="headerlink" title="方式一: 脚手架 (快捷、稳定)"></a>方式一: 脚手架 (快捷、稳定)</h3><ul><li>官方教程: <a href="https://doc.react-china.org/docs/add-react-to-a-new-app.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">参考链接1</a> <a href="https://github.com/facebook/create-react-app#create-react-app-" target="_blank" rel="noopener">参考链接2</a></li><li><p>执行命令:</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g create-react-app</span><br><span class="line">create-react-app my-app</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">cd my-app</span><br><span class="line">npm start</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span> 或使用以下命令 If you have npm 5.2.0+ installed, you may use npx instead.</span><br><span class="line">npx create-react-app my-app</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">cd my-app</span><br><span class="line">npm start</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h3 id="方式二-Webpack-步骤较多按下不表"><a href="#方式二-Webpack-步骤较多按下不表" class="headerlink" title="方式二:  Webpack (步骤较多按下不表)"></a>方式二:  Webpack (步骤较多按下不表)</h3><h2 id="元素渲染"><a href="#元素渲染" class="headerlink" title="元素渲染"></a>元素渲染</h2><p>元素是构成 React 应用的最小单位。</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> element = &lt;h1&gt;Hello, world&lt;/h1&gt;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>渲染元素</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> React <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">'react'</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> ReactDOM <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">'react-dom'</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> element = <span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span>Hello, world<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">ReactDOM.render(</span><br><span class="line">  element,</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">document</span>.getElementById(<span class="string">'root'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>React和ReactDOM为以下入口文件代码默认导包</p></blockquote><h2 id="组件及组件状态"><a href="#组件及组件状态" class="headerlink" title="组件及组件状态"></a>组件及组件状态</h2><p>组件可以将界面分割成一些的独立的、可复用的组成部分，我们只需专注于构建每一个单独的部分。按钮，对话框，列表，输入框都是组件。</p><p>组件从概念上看就像是函数，它可以接收任意的输入值（称之为“props”），并返回一个需要在页面上展示的React元素。</p><h3 id="函数定义组件-无状态"><a href="#函数定义组件-无状态" class="headerlink" title="函数定义组件(无状态)"></a>函数定义组件(无状态)</h3><p>JavaScript函数</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">function Hello(props) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">return &lt;h1&gt;Hi, &#123;props.name&#125;&lt;/h1&gt;;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="类定义组件-有状态"><a href="#类定义组件-有状态" class="headerlink" title="类定义组件(有状态)"></a>类定义组件(有状态)</h3><p><a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Classes" target="_blank" rel="noopener">class由es6支持</a></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">class Hello extends React.Component &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    render() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">   return &lt;h1&gt;Hi, &#123;this.props.name&#125;&lt;/h1&gt;;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>以上两个组件效果在React中相同</p><blockquote><p>注意： <strong>组件名首字母必须大写</strong></p></blockquote><h3 id="组合组件"><a href="#组合组件" class="headerlink" title="组合组件"></a>组合组件</h3><p>组件之间可以相互引用, 通常把App组件作为根组件。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">function App(props) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    return (</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;h1&gt;&#123;props.team&#125;&lt;/h1&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;p&gt;成立时间: &#123;props.date.toLocaleString()&#125;&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;p&gt;成员&#123;props.count&#125;&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;Hello name=&quot;悟空&quot; /&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;Hello name=&quot;三藏&quot; /&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;Hello name=&quot;八戒&quot; /&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;Hello name=&quot;沙僧&quot; /&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    );</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">ReactDOM.render(</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;App team=&quot;西天取经团&quot; date=&#123;new Date()&#125; count=&#123;4&#125;/&gt;,</span><br><span class="line">    document.getElementById(&apos;root&apos;)</span><br><span class="line">);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>可在Chrome安装React插件查看结构</p><p>注意：<strong>组件的返回值只能有一个根元素, 所以用一个div包裹所有Hello元素</strong></p></blockquote><h3 id="Props-属性"><a href="#Props-属性" class="headerlink" title="Props 属性"></a>Props 属性</h3><blockquote><p>props有两种输入方式：<strong>字符串“”</strong> ， <strong>大括号{}</strong></p><p>props不可修改，<strong>属性只读</strong>， 强行修改会报错</p></blockquote><h3 id="State-状态"><a href="#State-状态" class="headerlink" title="State 状态"></a>State 状态</h3><h4 id="自动更新时钟"><a href="#自动更新时钟" class="headerlink" title="自动更新时钟"></a>自动更新时钟</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">function tick() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    const element = (</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;h1&gt;时钟&lt;/h1&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;h2&gt;current: &#123;new Date().toLocaleString()&#125;&lt;/h2&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    )</span><br><span class="line">    ReactDOM.render(</span><br><span class="line">        element,</span><br><span class="line">        document.getElementById(&apos;root&apos;)</span><br><span class="line">    );</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">setInterval(tick, 1000);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>应用一般只进行一次<code>ReactDOM.render()</code>渲染</p></blockquote><ul><li>封装时钟</li><li>函数-&gt;类 / 定义局部状态属性</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">class Clock extends React.Component &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    constructor(props) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        super(props);</span><br><span class="line">        this.state = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            date: new Date(),</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;;</span><br><span class="line">        setInterval(() =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            this.tick()</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;, 1000);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    tick() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        // 更新date</span><br><span class="line">        this.setState(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            date: new Date()</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;)</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    render() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        return (</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;h1&gt;Hi, clock Component state new!&lt;/h1&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;h2&gt;current: &#123;this.state.date.toLocaleString()&#125;&lt;/h2&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        );</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">ReactDOM.render(</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;Clock /&gt;,</span><br><span class="line">    document.getElementById(&apos;root&apos;)</span><br><span class="line">);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><ol><li>state只能在构造函数初始化 <code>this.state={...}</code></li><li>通过<code>this.setState({...})</code>更新并渲染组件</li><li>调用<code>setState</code>时， React会将新的state合并到当前的state中</li></ol></blockquote><h2 id="组件生命周期"><a href="#组件生命周期" class="headerlink" title="组件生命周期"></a>组件生命周期</h2><p><img src="http://oi5nqn6ce.bkt.clouddn.com/18-4-11/9868593.jpg" alt="React中组件的生命周期"></p><blockquote><p>在componentDidMount初始化任务</p><p>在componentWillUnmount清理任务</p></blockquote><h2 id="事件处理"><a href="#事件处理" class="headerlink" title="事件处理"></a>事件处理</h2><h3 id="函数定义组件"><a href="#函数定义组件" class="headerlink" title="函数定义组件"></a>函数定义组件</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">function ActionButton() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    function handleClick(e) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        console.log(&apos;The Button was clicked.&apos;);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    return (</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;button onClick=&#123;handleClick&#125;&gt;按我&lt;/button&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    );</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="类定义组件"><a href="#类定义组件" class="headerlink" title="类定义组件"></a>类定义组件</h3><ul><li>注意以下两种写法的区别</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">class App extends React.Component &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    handleClick(e)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        console.log(this);</span><br><span class="line">        console.log(&quot;handleClick!&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    render() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        return (</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                    &lt;button onClick=&#123;this.handleClick&#125;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        按钮1 &#123;&apos;&#123;this.handleClick&#125;&apos;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">                    &lt;/button&gt;   </span><br><span class="line">                &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                    &lt;button onClick=&#123;() =&gt; this.handleClick()&#125;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        按钮2 箭头函数 &#123;&quot;&#123;() =&gt; this.handleClick()&#125;&quot;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">                    &lt;/button&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;/div&gt;  </span><br><span class="line">            &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        );</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>默认语法：类的方法默认不会绑定 this，也就是说在handleClick内部的this为undefined</p><p>箭头式语法：在每次App渲染时都会创建一个新的回调函数，可能会造成子组件的额外渲染</p></blockquote><ul><li>默认语法this问题解决方案：事件绑定 / 属性初始化器语法：</li></ul><ol><li><p>在<strong>构造函数绑定</strong>this</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">constructor(props) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    super(props);</span><br><span class="line">this.handleClick = this.handleClick.bind(this);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>使用 <strong>属性初始化器</strong> 语法 声明handleClick</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">handleClick = () =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    this.setState(preState =&gt; (&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        count: preState.count + 1</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;))</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><ul><li>计数器游戏</li></ul><h2 id="注意事项："><a href="#注意事项：" class="headerlink" title="注意事项："></a>注意事项：</h2><ul><li><p>组件名首字母必须大写</p></li><li><p>组件的返回值只能有一个根元素</p></li><li><p>props属性是只读的</p></li></ul>]]></content>
      
